"539","York, NY 10017 T: (646) 471 3000, F: (813) 286 6000,"
"540","www.pwc.com/us"
"541","This report is intended solely for the information and use"
"542","of management and the Board of Directors of Value Line"
"543","Larger Companies Focused Fund, Inc. and the Securities"
"544","and Exchange Commission and is not intended to be and"
"545","should not be used by anyone other than these specified"
"546","parties."
